{"word":"εἰρωνεύομαι","slug":"εἰρωνεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰρωνεύομαι</b></el> <el>(εἰρωνεύομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:εἴρων'><el>εἴρων</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to dissemble</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>feign ignorance</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: generally, <i>to dissemble, shuffle</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}